#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/main/guides/native-transport-reference.adoc
msgid "Default behavior"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/native-transport-reference.adoc
msgid ""
"When both epoll and io_uring are available on the classpath, Quarkus prefers **epoll** in `auto` mode.\n"
"This default prioritizes stability over experimental features."
msgstr ""

